@mikebotazzo please check your db connection and follow http://airbnb.io/caravel/installation.html
Also make sure you have followed these steps:

# Initialize the database

caravel db upgrade

# Create default roles and permissions

caravel init

# Load some data to play with

caravel load_examples

After that you can manually check your sqlite db to see if its populated. OperationalError: (sqlite3.OperationalError) no such table: dbs [SQL: u'SELECT count(?) AS count_1 \nFROM dbs'] [parameters: ('*',)] means the expected table is not in the db. So make sure you are pointing to right db settings in config.py
dbs table reference is coming from here: https://github.com/airbnb/caravel/blob/master/caravel/models.py#L294
